Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡簽名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在舊校舍搞什麼活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聚集一定的人數就無法拿到使用許可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很有趣吧  是笹田的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:01:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到高傲的班長要舉辦鬼怪大會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確定後跟你聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼了  突然慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不追過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏目玲子大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  玲子是我祖母  她已經去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交出來就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你這種低級妖怪能使用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有他死後友人帳歸我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我已經預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要消失的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾吧  不知天高地厚的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝禮就要七辻屋的包子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為友人帳而找上門的妖怪有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種是像剛才一樣想統治被寫了名字的妖怪而來搶友人帳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種則是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來討回寫在友人帳上的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個包子多少都吃得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  又歸還名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳越來越薄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸還名字後非常疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我拿到時還能剩幾隻呢  乾脆吃了這小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了哦  你這隻冒牌招財貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨開朗而溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋叔叔話比較少  但一直很溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不想給他們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃呢  貓咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這可添了個大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不吃剩飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  看來是個美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這是牙痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  真是美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心嗆到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好塔子阿姨他們看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  請把名字還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看你不是露神老頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為變小了我沒認出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  你是斑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼變成這副可笑的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵囉嗦  我吃了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守護喲  昭顯其名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跟後面一張黏在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  完全黏在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是米粒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米粒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子總是馬馬虎虎的  一邊吃飯一邊玩友人帳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…別硬拉開  皮膚像針刺一樣痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字被破壞身體就會裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉的話身體也會變成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦  抱歉了  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種情況  請你放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  可以來洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能如此無情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為揭不下來啊  我想還也還不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法吧  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法就是沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神就住在前面的七森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我拿來我就帶了  但這東西用來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一  反正先收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好心  沒摔壞的話就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也吃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  那我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候如果能作出更好的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭自己的不善言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老太太活不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息不太美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是露神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  露出這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神不只是名字  而是真正的神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  昨天做了那麼多失禮的事  會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子啊  你怎麼做這種遭天譴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙知道你是真正的神明驚慌失措了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  露神…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被稱為神明  其實以前我是住在這祠堂的無家可歸的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前這裡遭過嚴重的乾旱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:10:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的年輕人擔憂慘狀  向這個祠堂祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧第二天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後村人就把這個祠堂拜為露神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還放上很多供品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察覺到時已經充滿了力量  身體也變得像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看到他時身體還跟人類一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在人跡罕至了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以憑藉信仰成長的身體也縮小成這般模樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你桃子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子我也有哦  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到小花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她叫小花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是現在唯一會來這裡叩拜的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要把黏在一起的名字也歸還掉就不用強行揭開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不認識另一個妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗給玲子後我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說下一個被奪走名字的妖怪後我為了痛快去看過他的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  畫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字雖然不記得了  他是長這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我畫得真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…毛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他住在參之塚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陰影之主  利用陰影移動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼  嘲笑我的畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始在參之塚尋找這隻妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但花了好幾天也沒能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  好像很睏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索太累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  小花她看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在能感覺到呼吸的咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來參拜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  最近好像只有我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還怕露神大人寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從什麼時候開始來參拜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別見笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺自己見過一次露神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子學校放學回家路上  也是像今天一樣的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平時一樣參拜完抬起頭時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到祠堂後面有一隻腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嚇了一跳  但我裝作沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後看到戴著老翁面具的人很舒服地坐著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了句今天真是好天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就要回答說是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺到被人類看見露神大人就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在還在想  如果當時大膽地回答了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為露神大人總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一定會寂寞難耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少應該用聲音回應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人…很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚做惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的內心有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟弱的心會呼喚魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想丟掉性命就時刻不能放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我來說還是你早點丟掉性命  讓我早點拿到友人帳比較開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再睡傻就拔掉你尾巴上的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被妖怪說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那傢伙果然在這山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出聲叫他就跑了  但應該還沒走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  兵分兩路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼麻煩的東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙  他主動出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟畫完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話  分明一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個字是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  用鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用陽光反射  弄暈他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上前來取食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏過我就給你食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者把我吃掉也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玲子  你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濯  露神  把名字還給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供品不會一直持續的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上今天就連一個桃子都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類就是嚴厲和無情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著力量還在找個更好的住處比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦被愛過  去愛過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經能走路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫濯的妖怪  利用陰影來到村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為拿走剩飯的回報會幫那家人洗完盤子才離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你調查過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在街上連晚上也很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再見到他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山裡也有同伴  跟人類斷絕來往  那傢伙也輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神  我帶桃子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變小了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發光了  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花長年患病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近來一次也不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花是最後一個信奉我的人類  她走了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來信奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天來雖然很難  但我也會來叩拜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:20:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  夏目大人  你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟小花一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  一直僅僅是看著她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣終於…終於感覺能夠觸及她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花她聽見了…你的聲音  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論以前還是現在  都覺得人類真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你做什麼啊  好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種會遭天譴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡什麼都沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天沒有  也許明天就有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的心最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  這隻蠢貓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是招財貓啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵什麼喵  把包子還我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  慢著  包子小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我買的吧  等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵～喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  八原的妖怪們哭著說被人類欺負了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能看見妖怪的人做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是田沼要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:50.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}八原的怪人


